<div style="padding-left:10px; padding-bottom:5px; padding-top:2px; font-size:100%">
<p><b> Dagaaba </b>Dagaaba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo boɔloo. Dagaaba taa la lɛ ba naŋ maŋ boɔle ba neɛ bee taaba soba ka neɛ tõɔ wɛl ba taa. Dagaaba kɔkɔre la ka ba boɔlɔ ka Dagaare. Ka a wuli ka noba naŋ na yele a kɔkɔre e la Dagaaba. Dagaaba are ko la nenyaga a ba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo poɔŋ. Noba mine maŋ boɔlɔ la ka a nenyeni e Dagao, ka ba mine meŋ yeli ka Dagara. Ama pãã yi la a zie na o soba naŋ yi, lɛnso ka a boɔloo ba yi taa kyɛ kɔkɔre yeni la o zaa.</p>

    Yɛŋ duori-zaalaa zie neɛzaa naŋ na baŋ wane o teɛroŋ.
    A Dagaare Wikipiideɛ taa la 5,974 gampɛlɛ, yɛŋ duor-mɔla bɔzie.

    A yi zenɛ kyɛ gɛrɛ Atekele

    Dagaaba Dagaaba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo boɔloo. Dagaaba taa la lɛ ba naŋ maŋ boɔle ba neɛ bee taaba soba ka neɛ tõɔ wɛl ba taa. Dagaaba kɔkɔre la ka ba boɔlɔ ka Dagaare. Ka a wuli ka noba naŋ na yele a kɔkɔre e la Dagaaba. Dagaaba are ko la nenyaga a ba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo poɔŋ. Noba mine maŋ boɔlɔ la ka a nenyeni e Dagao, ka ba mine meŋ yeli ka Dagara. Ama pãã yi la a zie na o soba naŋ yi, lɛnso ka a boɔloo ba yi taa kyɛ kɔkɔre yeni la o zaa.

    ...kyɛ bee kane gaa tɔɔre
    A yi zenɛ kyɛ gɛrɛ Atekele

    Atekele soŋ

    Abdul-Rashid Hassan Pelpuo e la Ghanaian pɔleteesa kaŋa. Pampana ŋa o na la a begemaala gbɛbɔge naŋ are ko a Wa Central Gbandige naŋ be a Ɔpa Wɛse Irigyin a Ghana poɔ.

    ......Kyɛ bee Kanne gaa tɔɔre

    Fo baŋɛɛ la...?
    • Wiyaala e la Gaana yieloŋ ŋmeɛrɛ. O maŋ sɛge la yiele meŋ. O e la Sisaala?
    • Wa e la a Upper West Region tenkpoŋ. Be ka a Wa Naayiri a be?
    • University of Education, Winneba ela Univeniti naŋ be Winneba, Central irigyin, Gaana. O piili la 1992 a yi gɔbena( PNDC merɛ 322)?
    • Upper West Region waala Gaana irigyine kaŋa naŋ be a Gaana sazuŋ?
    • Wa West Desekyere e la a desekyere pie ne yeni kaŋa naŋ be Ɔpa Wɛse Irigyiŋ poɔ, Ghana?

|  ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/HSutvald2.svg/40px-HSutvald2.svg.png) A yi zenɛ kyɛ gɛrɛ Atekele **Dagaaba** Dagaaba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo boɔloo. Dagaaba taa la lɛ ba naŋ maŋ boɔle ba neɛ bee taaba soba ka neɛ tõɔ wɛl ba taa. Dagaaba kɔkɔre la ka ba boɔlɔ ka Dagaare. Ka a wuli ka noba naŋ na yele a kɔkɔre e la Dagaaba. Dagaaba are ko la nenyaga a ba laŋkpeɛbo ane a kɔkɔre zannoo poɔŋ. Noba mine maŋ boɔlɔ la ka a nenyeni e Dagao, ka ba mine meŋ yeli ka Dagara. Ama pãã yi la a zie na o soba naŋ yi, lɛnso ka a boɔloo ba yi taa kyɛ kɔkɔre yeni la o zaa. [...kyɛ bee kane gaa tɔɔre](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dagaaba "Dagaaba") [A yi zenɛ kyɛ gɛrɛ Atekele](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Featured_Articles?action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Featured Articles \(a pɛll ba tona\)") ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/HSbra2.svg/40px-HSbra2.svg.png) Atekele soŋ [![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/ABDUL-RASHID_HASSAN_PELPUO.jpg/120px-ABDUL-RASHID_HASSAN_PELPUO.jpg)](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Duoro_k%C9%94re:ABDUL-RASHID_HASSAN_PELPUO.jpg)ABDUL-RASHID HASSAN PELPUO **Abdul-Rashid Hassan Pelpuo** e la [Ghanaian pɔleteesa](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%C9%94litise%C9%9B%C5%8B?action=edit&redlink=1 "Pɔlitiseɛŋ \(a pɛll ba tona\)") kaŋa. Pampana ŋa o na la a begemaala gbɛbɔge naŋ are ko a [Wa Central Gbandige](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wa_Central_constituency "Wa Central constituency") naŋ be a [Ɔpa Wɛse Irigyin](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Upper_West_Region "Upper West Region") a [Ghana](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana "Ghana") poɔ. [......Kyɛ bee Kanne gaa tɔɔre](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abdul-Rashid_Pelpuo "Abdul-Rashid Pelpuo")[A yi zenɛ kyɛ gɛrɛ Atekele](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Good_Articles?action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Good Articles \(a pɛll ba tona\)") ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/46/Bluebg_rounded.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/Book_red%3B_question_marks.svg/40px-Book_red%3B_question_marks.svg.png) Fo baŋɛɛ la...?
  * **[Wiyaala](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiyaala "Wiyaala")** e la Gaana yieloŋ ŋmeɛrɛ. O maŋ sɛge la yiele meŋ. O e la Sisaala?
  * **[Wa](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wa "Wa")** e la a Upper West Region tenkpoŋ. Be ka a Wa Naayiri a be?
  * **[University of Education, Winneba](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Education,_Winneba "University of Education, Winneba")** ela Univeniti naŋ be Winneba, [Central irigyin](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Central_Region "Central Region"), [Gaana](https://dga.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghana "Ghana"). O piili la 1992 a yi gɔbena( PNDC merɛ 322)?
